  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a cooking journey, while enjoying a summer atmosphere of a coastal town.  Whether to sprint towards new challenges, or take a leisurely approach is up to you. And don't worry about profitability, here the only thing we care about is cooking food.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/21deee3e0d5d83f979f4ee7799ef907a.poster.avif?t=1731079593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/21deee3e0d5d83f979f4ee7799ef907a.webm?t=1731079593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/21deee3e0d5d83f979f4ee7799ef907a.mp4?t=1731079593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete orders requested by your customer by carefully preparing a variety of items, such as:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fries</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soda</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ice Cream</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main Dishes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serving perfectly made orders and dishes is needed in order to progress towards Challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/e4dfc947cde363488e013e92f1b26781.poster.avif?t=1731079593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/e4dfc947cde363488e013e92f1b26781.webm?t=1731079593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/e4dfc947cde363488e013e92f1b26781.mp4?t=1731079593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dish Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Affirm your mastery of these main dishes by completing their challenges and progress towards next goal:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hot Dogs <strong>→</strong> Sandwiches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sandwiches <strong>→</strong> Burgers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Burgers <strong>→</strong> Pizza</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pizza <strong>→</strong> Final Challenge</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/9ad12b0307d491c098a295f7421e43d7.poster.avif?t=1731079593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/9ad12b0307d491c098a295f7421e43d7.webm?t=1731079593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/9ad12b0307d491c098a295f7421e43d7.mp4?t=1731079593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Goal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete  Final Challenge that will REALLY test how far you've come as a chef.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a cooking journey, while enjoying a summer atmosphere of a coastal town.  Whether to sprint towards new challenges, or take a leisurely approach is up to you. And don't worry about profitability, here the only thing we care about is cooking food.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/21deee3e0d5d83f979f4ee7799ef907a.poster.avif?t=1731079593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/21deee3e0d5d83f979f4ee7799ef907a.webm?t=1731079593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/21deee3e0d5d83f979f4ee7799ef907a.mp4?t=1731079593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete orders requested by your customer by carefully preparing a variety of items, such as:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fries</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soda</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ice Cream</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main Dishes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serving perfectly made orders and dishes is needed in order to progress towards Challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/e4dfc947cde363488e013e92f1b26781.poster.avif?t=1731079593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265940/extras/e4dfc947cde363488e013e92f1b26781.webm?t=173